item.title: How do I delete Global Objects on [PI] Source? + Commands! :D?
item.dc:creator: @James-RevolutionX James-RevolutionX
item.description:
@James-RevolutionX wrote:

Deleting global objects is easy on a PI go into source->server-> world->objects (something similar) then scroll down to objectmanager when you open it up scroll down and there should be some coords such as:
(1, 5765, 5656) copy and paste a line then put your coords in and instead of a 1 do -1 that means delete the object.
